<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>SATELLITE IMAGE PRODUCTS and REMOTE SENSING</H1>
<center>
<p><I><A HREF="/geospace/hmgg.html">zur deutschen Version</A></i>
<p><IMG SRC="/myicons/em_spectrum.gif" ><BR>
<BR><h3><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Find information about our </FONT>
<a href="/geospace/act_e.html">NEW PRODUCTS!</a></H3>
</center>
<CENTER><P><IMG SRC="/myicons/em_spectrum.gif" ></center>
<P><IMG SRC="/images/sbgsmall.gif" HSPACE=20  ALIGN=LEFT><FONT COLOR="#000000">
<P>Geospace offers Remote Sensing Services and Remote Sensing Products
to public institutions and the private sector. Besides <A HREF="/geospace/progis_e.html">feasibility
studies and data evaluation projects</A>, the main fields of activities
are the production of Satellite Imagery from all over the world, Satellite
Image Maps and Satellite Image Atlases. You can ask us to search our <A HREF="/geospace/proima_e.html">Satellite
image archive</A> or order directly via e-mail from our standard <A HREF="/geospace/ordere.html">Satellite
image maps, atlases and CD-ROM product line</A>. (The image shows the center of Salzburg as 
viewed from a height of 700km, a detail of the satellite image map &quot;Salzburg-City&quot;)
<br clear=left>
<p><center><IMG SRC="/myicons/em_spectrum.gif" ></center><BR>
<BR></P>
<P>We are pleased to serve up the following additional informations: </P>
<UL>
<H4><IMG SRC="/myicons/gold.gif" ><A HREF="/geospace/profil_e.html"> GEOSPACE
- The Austrian Satellite Remote Sensing Company (profile)</A></H4>
<H4><IMG SRC="/myicons/gold.gif" ><A HREF="/geospace/produc_e.html"> GEOSPACE
- Products &amp; Services</A></H4>
<H4><IMG SRC="/myicons/gold.gif" ><A HREF="/geospace/gallery.html"> Satellite
Image Picture Gallery</A></H4>
</UL>
<CENTER><P><IMG SRC="/myicons/em_spectrum.gif" ><BR>
<BR>
Satellite image data from all civil systems can be ordered via the <BR>
<B><A HREF="http://www.ofd.ac.at/ofd/hmofd_e.html">Austrian Remote Sensing
Data Center <BR></a>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="/myicons/em_spectrum.gif" ><BR>
</B>
<p><I>&copy; by Geospace Austria / <A HREF="mailto:beckel@geospace.co.at">beckel@geospace.co.at</A>
<BR>
last modified 96/12/16 </I></P></CENTER>
