<HEAD>
<TITLE>Geospace Products and Services/GIS</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY background="/images/logoemb.gif"> 
<CENTER>  
<A HREF="/geospace/hmge.html"><IMG SRC="/images/logosmall.gif"></a>   
<H3><I>GEOSPACE Products and Services</I></H3>
<HR>
<H2>Satellite Image Data Evaluation and Interpretation for Information Systems</H2>
<HR>
<I> Diese Seite ist auch in <A HREF="/geospace/progis_g.html"> deutscher Sprache</A> verf&uuml;gbar </I><HR>
</CENTER>
<DL><i>GEOSPACE</i> has a long experience in producing satellite image maps and 
derived products for the integration in Geographic and Environmental Information 
Systems. It has a network of partners in various countries which complement the 
expertise of the company. Continous monitoring of the requiremtents of our 
customers and the cooperation with &ucirc;international research institutes 
secure the quality of our services.</DL>
<P>
Projects all over the world have been conducted using remote sensing data 
for various studies in the areas of:
<P>
<ul>
<IMG SRC="/myicons/red_ball.gif"> Environmental Impact Studies & Environmental Monitoring</A></STRONG><BR>
<IMG SRC="/myicons/red_ball.gif"> Agriculture</A></STRONG><BR>
<IMG SRC="/myicons/red_ball.gif"> Forestry</A></STRONG><BR>
<IMG SRC="/myicons/red_ball.gif"> Land use and urban planning</A></STRONG><BR>
<IMG SRC="/myicons/red_ball.gif"> Resource Management</A></STRONG><BR>
</ul><P>
<H4>Examples:</H4>
<IMG SRC="/myicons/red_ball.gif"> <A HREF="/images/wien.gif"> soil coverage of the 
Viennese area as derived from satellite image data (173858 bytes)</A>
<BR>
<HR>
<IMG SRC="/buttons/go_next_btn.gif"><DT>
To get more information about the integration of satellite image data in your Geographic or Environmental Information system please contact us:
<P>
<center>
e-mail:<A HREF="mailto:beckel@geospace.co.at">beckel@geospace.co.at</A> <BR>
Tel. Nr.: ++43-662-458115<BR>
Fax: ++43-662-4581154<BR>
<P>
<HR>
<A HREF="/geospace/hmge.html"><IMG align=middle SRC="/images/logotiny.gif">
