<HEAD>
<TITLE>Geospace Products and Services/Imagery</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY background="/images/logoemb.gif">   
<CENTER>
<A HREF="/geospace/hmge.html"><IMG SRC="/images/logosmall.gif"></a>
<H3><I>Geospace Products and Services</I></H3>
    
<H2>Satellite Imagery from all over the World</H2>
<P>
</CENTER>
<HR>
Geospace holds a large archive of processed satellite image data from all over the world.
 If you are looking for a special region we can check if we have data available. The near
 real colour images are of exceptionally high quality, devolped by the company through
 more than twenty years of experience (visit the <A
HREF="/geospace/gallery.html"> picture gallery </A>). Many satisfied clients use
 our images for advertising, books and various publications, company reports or regional
 maps and posters.<br>
Our copyright fees depend on size, copies and print run.Please indicate the region you
 are interested in and we will be glad to search our archive and assist you in the selection
 of the right solution for your purposes.
<HR>
<i><B>Please mail to</B></i><br>
<A HREF="mailto:beckel@geospace.co.at">beckel@geospace.co.at</A><br>
<P><i><B>if you prefer to send us a fax or call:</STRONG></B></i><br>
<DL>
<ul>
Tel. Nr.: (+43 662) 458115<br>
Fax: (+43 662) 4581154</DL>
</ul>
<P>
<HR>
<center>
<A HREF="/geospace/hmge.html"><IMG align=middle SRC="/images/logotiny.gif">
<i>GEOSPACE</i> Home Page</A>
