<HTML>
<HEAD>
<CENTER>
<TITLE>Geospace Products and Services</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY background="/images/logoemb.gif">
<a href="/geospace/hmge.html"><IMG SRC="/images/logosmall.gif"></a>
<H2><i>GEOSPACE</i> Products and Services</H2>
<I><A HREF="/geospace/produc_g.html">zur deutschen Version</A></I>
<p><img src="/myicons/em_spectrum.gif">
</CENTER>
<P><i>GEOSPACE</i> Austria produces Satellite Image Maps
   and Satellite Image Atlases. The company holds a large archive of satellite
   images from all over the world.<BR>
<P>
<A HREF="/ofd/hmofd_e.html">Raw satellite image data</A> from SPOT, LANDSAT, ERS-1, NOAA, Meteosat, etc. satellites are processed into real natural colour images and cartographic products. These images - presenting an extraordinary view of our world - are available in printed, photographic or digital form. <BR>
<HR>
 If you would like to know more about one product group, please
 select.<BR>
<B>You can order our products directly via e-mail or just ask for more information about images of a certain region.</B></P>
<UL>
<H4><IMG SRC="/myicons/red_ball.gif">
<A HREF="/geospace/act_e.html">New products</A></H4>
<H4><IMG SRC="/myicons/red_ball.gif"><A HREF="/geospace/ordere.html">  Satellite image maps, Posters, & Atlases off the shelf (order form)</A></H4>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="/geospace/ordere.html#karte">Satellite image maps</A><br>
example: <a href="/images/mapsbg.jpg"> satellite image map of the county of Salzburg</a></LI>

<LI><A HREF="/geospace/ordere.html#poster">Satellite image posters</A><br>
example: <a href="/images/europe.gif"> satellite image poster of Europe</a></LI>

<LI><A HREF="/geospace/ordere.html#atlas">Satellite image atlases and books</A></LI>

<LI><A HREF="/geospace/ordere.html#folien">Transparent series</A></LI>

<LI><A HREF="/geospace/ordere.html#kalen">Calendars</A></LI>

<LI><A HREF="/geospace/ordere.html#galler">Art Gallery</A></LI>

<LI><A HREF="/geospace/cdrome.html">Satellite Atlas on CD-ROM</A></LI>
</UL>
<H4><IMG SRC="/myicons/red_ball.gif"><A HREF="/geospace/proima_e.html">  Satellite Imagery from all over the world</A></H4>
<H4><IMG SRC="/myicons/red_ball.gif"><A HREF="/geospace/progis_e.html">  Satellite Image data Evaluation and Interpretation as Input for Information Systems</A></H4>
</UL>
<center>
<p><img src="/myicons/em_spectrum.gif">
