<H2 ALIGN=CENTER><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">The unique digital Satellite Image
Atlas</font></H2>
<CENTER><h1>CD-ROM SATELLITEN-ATLAS <br>by <i>GEOSPACE</i> and HEROLD</h1></CENTER>

<CENTER><P><B><I>now available: Edition Austria and Edtion
Germany</I> (in German language only)</B></P></CENTER>

<P>Look down on the Earth from space. Zoom in and fly over
continents, regions, countries or cities. The &quot;Satelliten Atlas&quot;
on CD is a combination of satellite images and world atlas - with images
in billant colours and with lots of animating features.</P>

<P>
<HR WIDTH="100%"><B>The CD-ROM Satellite Image Atlas contains: <BR>
<p><FONT COLOR="#008000">Satellite images in near natural colours:</FONT>&nbsp;<BR>
</B>- Full coverage of the Earth with 5 km ground resolution<BR>
- Full coverage of Europe with 1 km ground resolution<BR>
- Full coverage of Austria (Edition &Ouml;sterreich) or Germany (Edition
Deutschland) with 30 m ground resolution<BR>
- Selected landscapes and cities (e.g. in Austria: Austrian capitals) with
10 m ground resolution<BR>
- Several satellite images worldwide (hot spots) with 30 m ground resolution<BR>
<p><B><FONT COLOR="#000080">Additional Information:<BR>
</FONT></B>- Aerial photographs<BR>
- Interpretative texts and geographical texts<BR>
- Data bases: cities, landscapes, waterways, oceans, borders, mountains,
etc.<BR>
- Introduction into the programm<BR>
- Multimedia introduction into satellite remote sensing (animation programme)<BR>
<p><B><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Functions:<BR>
</FONT></B>- Continous display of coordinates, diplay of grid net <BR>
- Legend to choose display of additional information (texts, cities, landscapes,
borders, oceans, continents, etc.).<BR>
- Name register with automatic search function <BR>
- Distance measurment<BR>
- Different zooming stages and scrolling<BR>
- help function and lots more.</P>

<P><B>System requriements:<BR>
</B>*PC with 486 processor or higher<BR>
*Operating system MS-DOS from version 6.0<BR>
*MS Windows from Version 3.1 or higher<BR>
*8 MB RAM<BR>
*Minimum 256 colour display<BR>
*Minimum 800 x 600 pixel screen resolution<BR>
* Double speed CD-ROM drive<BR>
* For some special functions a 16 MB RAM and a sound card is required.
Without this the running of this special functions is not guaranteed..<BR>
</P>

<P>
<HR>Order the<B> &quot;Satelliten Atlas&quot;</B> directly via
<A HREF="mailto:beckel@geospace.co.at">e-mail</A>.<B> Edition &Ouml;sterreich
or Edition Deutschland - at the price of ATS&nbsp;790,-</B> <B>each</B>
(excl. packaging and shipping)</P>

