<HTML>
<HEAD>
<CENTER>
<TITLE>Service OFD</TITLE></HEAD><BODY background="/images/ofd12b.gif">
<A HREF="/ofd/hmofd_e.html"><IMG SRC="/images/ofd12.gif"></a>   
<H2>Services of the Austrian Remote Sensing Data Center (OFD)</H2> 
<HR>
<I> There is a <A HREF="/ofd/ofd_serv.html"> German version</A> of this text available </I><HR>
</CENTER>
As the use of Earth Observation data from satellites is increasing in all areas of 
science, administration and economy and new products and services are developed 
continuously, the <B>"Techno-Z Salzburg Research"</B> Association together with 
<a href="http://geospace.co.at/"><B><i>GEOSPACE Austria</i></B></a>, decided to 
establish the <B>"Austrian Remote Sensing Data Center - A Research Institute of 
the Salzburg Research Association"</B> (OFD).<P>
<H4>The Austrian Remote Sensing Data Center (OFD) is official Distributor in 
Austria for:</H4>
<UL>
<IMG SRC="/myicons/red_ball.gif"><STRONG>        SPOTImage</STRONG><BR>
<IMG SRC="/myicons/red_ball.gif"><STRONG>        Eurimage and EOSAT</STRONG>(Landsat, JERS, Resurs, KFA, KVR)<BR>
<IMG SRC="/myicons/red_ball.gif"><STRONG>        ESA-Earthnet</STRONG> (ERS-1, ERS-2)<BR>
<IMG SRC="/myicons/red_ball.gif"><STRONG>        Radarsat</STRONG><BR>
<IMG SRC="/myicons/red_ball.gif"><STRONG>        Worldmap Priroda</STRONG><BR>
<IMG SRC="/myicons/red_ball.gif"><STRONG>        Euromap (IRS)</STRONG><BR>
</UL>
<P>The Austrian Remote Sensing Data Center (OFD) runs the Austrian fast delivery receiving station for ERS data.
<P>
<STRONG>The following services are offered by the OFD:</STRONG><BR>
<ul>
<IMG SRC="/newicons/images/Squares/yellow.gif"> Continuous information about developemtents in the area of Earth Observation from Space - technologies<BR>
<IMG SRC="/newicons/images/Squares/yellow.gif"> Consulting in the application and selection of satellite data<BR>
<IMG SRC="/newicons/images/Squares/yellow.gif"> Worldwide data bank search for suitable data <BR>
<IMG SRC="/newicons/images/Squares/yellow.gif"> Carrying out Quick-Look order to help you to choose the most interesting scenes<BR>
<IMG SRC="/newicons/images/Squares/yellow.gif"> Carrying out data order, distribution of data<BR>
<IMG SRC="/newicons/images/Squares/yellow.gif"> Information about special prices of satellite data providers<BR>
</ul>
<HR>
<IMG SRC="/newicons/images/ButSmall/right.gif"><DT>We search for you our data base and the data bases of our partners to find the suitable data for your special application - 
 <STRONG><A HREF="/ofd/data_e.html">Data Search Request</A></STRONG>
<HR>

<IMG SRC="/newicons/images/ButSmall/right.gif"><DT>
 You can order satellite image data directly via e-mail, please indicate your adress,
 telephone and fax-number and we will contact you immediately - 
 <STRONG><A HREF="mailto:satdata@ofd.ac.at">satdata@ofd.ac.at</A></STRONG>
<HR>
<IMG SRC="/newicons/images/ButSmall/right.gif"><DT>If you want to know more about
 satellite image data, the products of satellite data providers, prices, etc.,
 please call us or send us an e-mail, so that we can put you on our mailing list.
 We will be glad to inform you about special offers, developments and activities in
 the field of Earth Observation from Space.
<BR>
<DL>
<center>Tel.: ++43-662-458506<BR>
Fax: ++43-662-4581154<BR>
e-mail:<A HREF="mailto:satdata@ofd.ac.at">satdata@ofd.ac.at</A></center></DL>
<HR>
<P>
<center><A HREF="/ofd/hmofd_e.html"><IMG align="middle" 
SRC="/images/ofd06.gif"> OFD Homepage</A>
<br><br>
