<TITLE>Data Search</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY background="/images/ofd12b.gif">
<A HREF="/ofd/hmofd_e.html"><IMG SRC="/images/ofd12.gif"></a>
<H2>Data Search</H2>
<hr>
<I> Diese Seite ist auch in <A HREF="/ofd/data_g.html"> deutscher Sprache</A>
verf&uuml;gbar </I>
<HR></CENTER>
<P><B>Please send us the information about your application according to the above
 listed criteria (as far as possible) <A HREF="mailto: satdata@ofd.ac.at">
via e-mail</A> and we will search the suitable data for you: 
</b><P><HR>
<H3>Area Information:</H3>
<UL>
<LI>Region
<LI>N/S longitude
<LI>E/W latitutde
</UL>
<P><HR>
<H3>Application field, e.g.:</H3>
<UL>
Agriculture; Cartography; Coastal Monitoring; Diseaster Management; Forestry;
Gas, Oil, Mineral Exploration; Geology; Hydrology; Ice-monitoring; Interferometry; Landuse monitoring; Meteorology; Oceanography; Offshore operations; Pollution Control; Ship routing; Urban planning; Water-Resources;
</UL>
<P><HR>
  <H3>Resolution, e.g.:</H3>
<UL>
<LI>2 m   (KFA-3000)
<LI>5 m   (KFA-1000)
<LI>8 m   (MK-4)
<LI>10 m   (SPOT)
<LI>20 m   (SPOT, Kate-200)
<LI>30 m   (LANDSAT TM,MSS)
<LI>60 m   (LANDSAT TM, MSS)
</UL>
<P><HR>
  <H3>Age range</H3>
<UL>
<LI>0 - 2 years
<LI>0 - 4 years
<LI>other   
</UL>
<P><HR>
 <H3>Acceptable cloud coverage</H3>
<UL>
<LI>0 %
<LI>less than 10 %
<LI>less than 20 %
<LI>less than 30 %
<LI>less than 50 %
</UL>
<P>
<HR>
<H3>Quicklook:</H3>   yes/no   
<P><HR>
