</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>

<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Applications:</FONT></H2>

<P>Because of the seven spectral channels Landsat-TM data are especially
qualified for landuse classification, forestry and environmental studies
as well as for planning and control in resource-management. Landsat MSS
data can be an economical solution for various applications.</P>

<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Limitations:</FONT></H2>

<UL>
<LI><FONT COLOR="#000000">the optical sensor cannot penetrate the cloud
cover </FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT COLOR="#000000">limited resolution </FONT></LI>
</UL>

<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Special offers:</FONT></H2>
Regularily special conditions for archive data are offered.
Reductions for monitoring (several numbers of scenes of one area at different
acquisition times) are also available.
<P>
