<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Applications:</FONT></H2>

<P>Due to the high ground resolution these data are especially qualified
for applications in landuse-planning and cartography where detailed recognizeability
is required.</P>

<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Limitations:</FONT></H2>

<P>Compared to satellite remote sensing systems the Russian cameras do
not provide a contious coverage of the whole earth surface. Data are not
always available for certain areas but programming is possible.</P>

