<TD>
<CENTER><P>exabyte, CD-ROM</P></CENTER>
</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE></CENTER>

<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Applicatons:</FONT></H2>

<P>Because the Resurs-01 satellite is covering a surface of 600 x 600 km
these data is espacially suited for regional studies in the areas of:<BR>
- Agriculture and forestry<BR>
- Monitoring of costal zones<BR>
- Snow- and ice-monitoring</P>

<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Limitations:</FONT></H2>

<P>Completely cloud free scenes are rare because of scene size. </P>

<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Special offers:</FONT></H2>

<P>Special offers for monitoring. </P>

