<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Applications:</FONT></H2>

<P>Land use classification, landscape planning, cartography, agriculture,
forestry, environmental studies, management of resources, interferometry</P>

<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Limitations:</FONT></H2>

<P>Cloud coverage with optical data, software with radar data </P>

<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Special offers:</FONT></H2>

<P>Cheap data for research users - but complicated proposal procedure </P>

