</TR>
</TABLE></CENTER>

<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Applications:</FONT></H2>

<UL>
<LI>PAN-data: landscape planning, cartography, city planning, infrastructure
planning, delineation of objects (forestry), etc.</LI>

<LI>Multispectral data: cartography, studies in the area of agriculture,
forestry, environment, geology, resource management, etc.</LI>
</UL>

<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Limitations:</FONT></H2>

<P>cloud coverage</P>

