<TD>
<CENTER><P>30 m</P></CENTER>
</TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD><B>Scene size</B></TD>

<TD>
<CENTER><P>100 x 100 km</P></CENTER>
</TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD><B>Proposed maxim. scale</B></TD>

<TD>
<CENTER><P>1:100 000</P></CENTER>
</TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD><B>Costs</B></TD>

<TD>
<CENTER><P>from ECU 1.200 (for commercial use) </P></CENTER>
</TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD><B>Quicklook</B></TD>

<TD>
<CENTER><P>no</P></CENTER>
</TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD><B>Datentr&auml;ger </B></TD>

<TD>
<CENTER><P>film, CD-ROM, exabyte, CCT</P></CENTER>
</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE></CENTER>

<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Applications:</FONT></H2>

<UL>
<LI>Especially suited for sea- and ice studies</LI>

<LI>Complementary information to optical data for land use classification,
forestry, etc. in areas with high cloud coverage</LI>

<LI>Generation of digital elevation models (interferometry)</LI>
</UL>

<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Limitations:</FONT></H2>

<P>- Software to process and evaluate the data</P>

<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Special offers:</FONT></H2>

<P>Special prices for scientific use (approx. half of the regular price)</P>

