<HEAD>

<TITLE>NCADD - History Directory</TITLE>

<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="R. Coleman, Occasional Designs">
<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.0z">
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<IMG SRC="graphics/histban.gif" ALT="History of NCADD" width=672  height=84><BR>
<BR>
<H3><IMG SRC="graphics/marty.gif" WIDTH=148 HEIGHT=200 ALIGN="MIDDLE"> Marty Mann, NCADD Founder</H3>
<P>
<B>&quotAn Alcoholic is someone whose drinking causes a problem in any department of his life.&quot</B><BR>
<BR>
<B>Marty Mann, <I>New Primer on Alcoholism</I> (1950)</B>
