<HEAD>

<TITLE>NCADD - Intervention Page</TITLE>

<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="R. Coleman, Occasional Designs">
<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.0z">
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<IMG SRC="graphics/interban.gif" ALT="National Intervention Network" width=672 height=84><BR>
<BR>
<H2>Does someone you care about have a problem with drinking or other drugs?</H2>
 <CENTER><IMG SRC="graphics/window.gif" width=205 height=250></CENTER><BR>
 <CENTER><H1>INTERVENTION MAY BE THE ANSWER</H1></CENTER>
  <P>
  Getting someone help who doesn't want help is what
  intervention is all about.  That's not always easy.
  <P>
  NCADD operates a National Intervention Network through many
  of its local Affiliates.  We can help you plan, rehearse and
  conduct an intervention.
  <P>
  <B>But you have to make the call and ask us for our help.  Do
  it for someone you know, or someone you love.</B><BR>
  <BR>
  <CENTER><IMG SRC="graphics/hopeline.gif" ALT="1-800-654-HOPE NATIONAL INTERVENTION NETWORK" WIDTH=500 HEIGHT=143></CENTER><BR>
  <BR>
  <H3><I>CURRENT AREAS OF SERVICE</I></H3>
<HR>
<TABLE WIDTH="80%">
<TR>
<TD>  
