<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="graphics/logomaj1.gif" ALT="NCADD Logo" WIDTH=670 HEIGHT=300></CENTER><BR>
<CENTER><A HREF="more.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/eih&h.gif" ALT="EDUCATION, INFORMATION, HELP AND HOPE" width=672 height=232 border=0></A></CENTER><BR>
<BR>
<CENTER><A HREF="more.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/logobut1.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 ALIGN="TOP"></A><A HREF="more.html"> NCADD - MORE ON OUR MISSION </A><A HREF="more.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/logobut1.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 ALIGN="TOP"></A></CENTER>
<BR>
<CENTER><TABLE WIDTH="100%">
<TR>
<TD ALIGN="CENTER"><A HREF="histdir.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/marty.gif" width=148 height=200></A><BR>
<B>Marty Mann, <A HREF="histdir.html">NCADD FOUNDER</A></B><BR></TD>
<TD ALIGN="CENTER"><A HREF="pardir.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/parents.gif" width=222 height=200></A><BR>
<B>INFORMATION FOR <A HREF="pardir.html">PARENTS</A></B><BR></TD>
</TR>
</TABLE></CENTER><BR><BR>
<CENTER><A HREF="youdir.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/kid1.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=302 HEIGHT=284></A><BR></CENTER>
<CENTER><B>INFORMATION FOR <A HREF="youdir.html">YOUTH</A></B></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>
<DL>
<DT><A HREF="policy.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/logobut1.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 ALIGN="TOP"></A><A HREF="policy.html"> ADVOCACY INFORMATION:</A><BR>
       <DD>Our Washington office opened more than 20 years ago to
       represent the interests of alcoholics, other addicted
       persons and their families.  Find out what's happening
       now at the federal government level and what action you
	 can take.<P>

  
<DT><A HREF="affildir.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/logobut1.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 ALIGN="TOP"></A><A HREF="affildir.html"> AFFILIATES:</A> <BR>
       <DD>With more than 130 councils around the country, we are
       uniquely positioned to provide a local perspective on
       alcoholism and other drug addictions.<P>

  
<DT><A HREF="defalc.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/logobut1.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 ALIGN="TOP"></A><A HREF="defalc.html"> DEFINITION OF ALCOHOLISM:</A> <BR>
       <DD>This comprehensive definition, published by the Journal
       of the American Medical Association in 1992, was
       developed by a group of the nation's most esteemed
       physicians working in the addictions field.<P>

  
<DT><A HREF="factsdir.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/logobut1.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 ALIGN="TOP"></A><A HREF="factsdir.html"> FACTS ABOUT ALCOHOLISM AND OTHER DRUG ADDICTIONS:</A> <BR>
       <DD>Statistical information with sources, ideal for use by
       the media or students doing reports.<P>

  
<DT><A HREF="healdir.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/logobut1.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 ALIGN="TOP"></A><A HREF="healdir.html"> HEALTH INFORMATION:</A> <BR>
       <DD>Recommendations about drinking from the US Dietary
       Guidelines and the Surgeon General of the United States.<P>

  
<DT><A HREF="histdir.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/logobut1.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 ALIGN="TOP"></A><A HREF="histdir.html"> HISTORY OF NCADD:</A> <BR>
       <DD>A look back at our effort to educate Americans that
       alcoholism is a preventable, treatable disease.<P>

  
<DT><A HREF="interven.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/logobut1.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 ALIGN="TOP"></A><A HREF="interven.html"> NATIONAL INTERVENTION NETWORK:</A> <BR>
       <DD>If you know someone who drinks too much or needs help
       with a drug problem, don't wait to do something.<P>

  
<DT><A HREF="newsdir.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/logobut1.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 ALIGN="TOP"></A><A HREF="newsdir.html"> NEWS FROM NCADD:</A> <BR>
       <DD>Information about our recent activities.<P>

  
<DT><A HREF="pardir.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/logobut1.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 ALIGN="TOP"></A><A HREF="pardir.html"> PARENTS INFORMATION:</A> <BR>
       <DD>Suggestions for communicating with your child about
       drinking.<P>

  
<DT><A HREF="pubs.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/logobut1.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 ALIGN="TOP"></A><A HREF="pubs.html"> PUBLICATIONS:</A> <BR>
       <DD>A complete list of our educational materials, including
       newsletters, pamphlets and posters.<P>

  
<DT><A HREF="randr.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/logobut1.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 ALIGN="TOP"></A><A HREF="randr.html"> RESOURCE & REFERRAL GUIDE:</A> <BR>
       <DD>An easy way to access other national organizations
       working in the field of alcoholism and other drug
       addictions.<P>

  
<DT><A HREF="youdir.html"><IMG SRC="graphics/logobut1.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 ALIGN="TOP"></A><A HREF="youdir.html"> YOUTH INFORMATION:</A> <BR>
       <DD>Hear what some young people are saying and take a test
       to find out how alcohol and other drugs may be
       affecting your life.
</DL>
