<HEAD>

<TITLE>NCADD - Affiliate Membership</TITLE>

<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="R. Coleman, Occasional Designs">
<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.0z">
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<IMG SRC="graphics/memhr.gif" ALT="AFFILIATE MEMBERSHIP" WIDTH=674 HEIGHT=50>
<P>
  Unite with the citizens in your community and across America
  who are fighting alcoholism and other drug addictions; who
  are working to influence the media, the federal, state and
  local governments by advocating prevention, intervention,
  research and treatment; and who are dedicated to ridding the
  disease of its stigma and its sufferers from their denial
  and shame. <BR>
    <BR>
  <IMG SRC="graphics/benhr.gif" ALT="BENEFITS OF AFFILIATION" WIDTH=674 HEIGHT=26><BR>
<P>
<TABLE>
<TR>
<TD>
  <UL>
  <LI>National Advocacy <BR> 
     -- Federal Government<BR> 
     -- National Media <BR>
     -- National Coalitions <BR>
  <BR>
  <LI><A HREF="pubs.html">Publications</A>/Communications <BR>
     -- FAX Action Alerts <BR>
     -- NCADD Amethyst <BR>
     -- NCADD Voice <BR>
     -- The Alcoholism Report <BR>
  <BR>
  <LI>Use of NCADD Name & <A HREF="history.html">Logo</A> <BR>
  <BR>
  <LI>National/Regional Conferences <BR>
  <BR>
  <LI>Reduced Fees at Conferences<BR>
</UL>
  </TD>
<TD>
<UL>
  <LI>National <A HREF="interven.html">Intervention</A> Network <BR>
  <BR>
  <LI>Discounts on NCADD Products<BR> 
     -- Fact Sheets <BR>
     -- Brochures <BR>
     -- Posters <BR>
     -- Video Tapes <BR>
  <BR>
  <LI>National Recognition for Programs, <BR>
   Volunteers, Donors and
  Executives<BR>
   <BR>
  <LI>Referrals from <B>(800) NCA-CALL</B><BR> 
  <BR>
  <LI>Ad Council Public Service Campaigns 
</UL>
   </TD>
</TR>
