<HR>
<H2>Science Reports</H2>
<P>Nirex, as  part of its efforts to ensure wide availability for its research
results, is publishing some of its Science Reports on this web-site. Other
Reports will be added shortly and it is intended to publish new Reports on a
regular basis. 
</P>
<P>These Reports are faithful replicas of the hard-copy originals.
</P>
<P>You will need The Acrobat reader from Adobe
<A HREF="http://www.adobe.com/acrobat/readstep.html"><IMG
SRC="getacro.jpg" WIDTH="88" HEIGHT="31"></A> There are Windows, Mac and Unix
versions available.</P>
<P>Each Report has embedded images - these are in black and white with low
image resolution to keep the overall report size down. </P>
<P>If you feel that you require better images, click on the black and white
representation in Acrobat and a corresponding image file for that Report will be
downloaded. These are typically over 1Mb in size. </P>
<P></P>
