<H3><A NAME="Nirex_in_Cumbria">Nirex - The Facts</A></H3>
<TABLE><TR><TD COLSTART="1"><A HREF="nirfx1.htm">Nirex
- What we do</A></TD>
<TD COLSTART="2"></TD></TR><TR><TD COLSTART="1"><A
HREF="nirfx2.htm">About Nirex</A></TD><TD COLSTART="2"></TD></TR>
<TR><TD COLSTART="1"><A HREF="nirfx3.htm">Source of
the waste</A></TD><TD COLSTART="2"></TD></TR><TR><TD COLSTART="1"><A
HREF="nirfx4.htm">How much waste is there?</A></TD><TD
COLSTART="2"></TD></TR><TR><TD COLSTART="1"><A
HREF="nirfx5.htm">Why bury the waste?</A></TD><TD
COLSTART="2"></TD></TR><TR><TD COLSTART="1"><A
HREF="nirfx6.htm">Containing the radioactivity</A></TD><TD
COLSTART="2"></TD></TR>
<TR><TD COLSTART="1"><A HREF="nirfx7.htm">The Rock
laboratory</A></TD><TD COLSTART="2"></TD></TR><TR><TD COLSTART="1"><A
