<H3>New Appointments at Nirex</H3>
<P></P>
<P>FOUR new directors have joined the Board of Nirex, the radioactive
waste disposal company.</P>
<P>They are: Dr Jean MacDonald, who is Company Secretary at Scottish
Nuclear Ltd and Head of Legal Services at British Energy plc;  Mr Stephen
Ogle, the Executive Director of  Finance and Commercial at Magnox Electric
plc;  Mr John Baxter, the Director, Nuclear Operations at the UKAEA; and Dr
Stuart Ward, who is Director of Business Support at Nuclear Electric Ltd.</P>
<P>Mr Peter Warry, formerly a nominee of  Nuclear Electric plc on the
Board, is now a nominee of Nuclear Electric Ltd.</P>
