<TD>10.</TD>
<TD VALIGN="TOP" WIDTH="50">i.</TD>
<TD>Whether, or the extent to which, the existence of other possible sites for
a repository is a consideration material to the determination of this appeal.</TD></TR>
<TR ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP">
