<P><A NAME="Table6.1"></A><I>TABLE 6.1: POTENTIAL VISUAL EFFECTS ON
SETTLEMENTS AND PROPERTIES WITHIN 1.5km OF THE CENTRE OF THE PLATFORM SITE</I></P>
<P><BR>*indicates properties more than 1.5km from the development investigated
to determine whether they have significant views of the proposed development.</P>
