30 November 1994</FONT></P>
<P>Economic and Environment<BR>Planning Division<BR>Cumbria County Council<BR>County
Offices<BR>Kendal<BR>Cumbria  LA9 4RQ<BR><BR></P>
<P>FOR THE ATTENTION OF MR JOHN HETHERINGTON<BR>ENVIRONMENTAL PLANNING MANAGER<BR><BR><BR></P>
