<P>RE: SUBMISSION OF FURTHER INFORMATION IN RESPECT OF AN ENVIRONMENTAL
STATEMENT<BR>ROCK CHARACTERISATION FACILITY, LAND ADJACENT TO LONGLANDS FARM<BR>GOSFORTH<BR><BR></P>
