<TD><FONT SIZE="-1">...concerned at increase in heavy traffic.</FONT></TD>
<TD><FONT SIZE="-1">The heaviest HGV flows are limited in duration to five
months at the start of construction and at site restoration. Mostly HGVs average
at about 5 to 20 vehicles per day in each direction. This does not represent a
significant increase in traffic on the A595(T).</FONT></TD></TR>
<TR ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP">
<TD COLSPAN="3"><FONT SIZE="-1">Source: PE/NRX/9 Reference 5, Document
COR/104: Report by the Director of Economy and Environment, Cumbria County
Council, December 1994.</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>
