<P>39. COR/409<BR>'Blight and Nuclear Facilities', 1995, <B>P</B><I>ieda</I>,
page 44, para 5.8</P>
<P>40. COR/406<BR>'Perceptions of West Cumbria as a Destination for Leisure
Travel and Inward Investment', 1994, University of Newcastle-Upon-tyne, page 6.</P>
<P>41. COR/406<BR>'Perceptions of West Cumbria as a Destination for Leisure
Travel and Inward Investment',  1994, University of Newcastle-Upon-tyne, page 7.</P>
<P>42. COR/406<BR>'Perceptions of West Cumbria as a Destination for Leisure
Travel and Inward Investment', 1994, University of  Newcastle-Upon-tyne, page
11.</P>
<P>43. NRX/10/9<BR>'Tourism Research in Cumbria', 1989, Cumbria Tourist Board
page 13.</P>
<P>44. NRX/10/10<BR>Perception of West Cumbria as a Destination for Inward
Investment, 1995, pages 5 and 8.</P>
<P>45. NRX/10/11<BR>'Feasibility Study for Siting of a Deep Repository Within
the Storurnan Municipality', 1995, SKB.</P>
<P>46. NRX/10/11<BR>'Feasibility Study for Siting of a Deep Repository Within
the Storuman Municipality', 1995, SKB, pages 81-105.</P>
<P ALIGN="LEFT"><A NAME="Appendix"></A><FONT SIZE="+2"><B>APPENDIX 1</B><BR><B>Model
Code of Employee Relations</B><BR><B>(Sections 1.0 - 6.0)</B></FONT></P>
<P><BR><BR></P>
<CENTER>
<P><B>UNITED KINGDOM NIREX LIMITED</B></P>
<P><B>ROCK CHARACTERISATION</B></P>
<P><B>FACILITY</B></P>
<P><B>MODEL CODE OF EMPLOYEE RELATIONS</B></P>
<P><B>PRACTICE FOR WORK ON THE RCF SITE</B></P></CENTER>
<P><BR></P>
